SUMMARY:Sunday Road Trip to Niagara Falls: Le Grand Cirque – MAXIMUM VEL
 OCITY! $50 total
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n***\n\n
 🎪🚗 **Sunday Road Trip to Niagara Falls: Le Grand Cirque – MAXIMUM 
 VELOCITY!** 🚗🎪\n\n**Sunday\, March 22**\n\nJoin us for a thrilling S
 unday getaway to **Niagara Falls** to experience **Le Grand Cirque: MAXIMU
 M VELOCITY** — a high-octane\, jaw-dropping spectacle at Fallsview Casin
 o Resort!\n\nTravel together in a comfortable **Kia Soul**\, complete with
  **snow tires** and **SiriusXM**\, and enjoy a relaxed road trip with grea
 t company before an unforgettable afternoon show.\n\nDepending on traffic 
 we may be able to sightsee a bit before the show\n\n***\n\n### ✨ **About
  the Show**\n\n**Le Grand Cirque: MAXIMUM VELOCITY** is an adrenaline-fuel
 ed cirque production packed with gravity-defying acrobatics\, daring aeria
 l acts\, incredible strength performances\, and breathtaking stunts perfor
 med by world-class artists. Fast-paced\, visually stunning\, and family-fr
 iendly\, this show delivers nonstop excitement from start to finish.\n🔗
  **Event details:**\n[https://fallsviewcasinoresort.com/events-and-promoti
 ons/schedule-of-events/le-grand-cirque.html](https://fallsviewcasinoresort
 .com/events-and-promotions/schedule-of-events/le-grand-cirque.html)\n\n***
 \n\n### 🕛 **Schedule**\n\n* **12:00 PM (Noon)** – Depart Toronto\n* *
 *3:00 PM** – Show starts\n* **\\~7:00 PM** – Return to Toronto\n\n***\
 n\n### 🚗 **What’s Included**\n\n* 🎟️ Show ticket\n* 🚘 Round-t
 rip transportation in a Kia Soul\n* 🎶 SiriusXM music for the drive\n\n*
 **\n\n### 💲 **Cost**\n\n**$50 total** (includes ticket and transportati
 on)\n👉 **Payment required in advance**\nPlease e-transfer $50 to: nicol
 asbello@yahoo.com\nYour spot is confirmed once payment is received.\n\n***
 \n\nSpace is limited\, so please RSVP **only if you’re fully committed**
 \, as tickets and transportation are arranged in advance.\nLet’s enjoy a
  fun Sunday road trip and an electrifying afternoon at the circus! 🎪✨
